Second Department,

October, 1944.

(October 2, 1944.) Lena Canter et al., Appellants, v. Frank Aranow, Respondent.

Motion for reargument granted and on reargument defendant’s application for leave to appeal to the Appellate Division is granted. [See 181 Misc. 947; ante, p. 779.] Present— Close, P. J., Carswell, Johnston, Lewis and Aldrich, JJ. [See 269 App. Div. 668.]
